                        <h5 class="center">About company</h5>

                        <p class="light">Our company is the best in the world. Our company is the best in the world. Our company is the best in the world.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">settings</i></h2>

                        <h5 class="center">About company</h5>

                        <p class="light">Our company is the best in the world. Our company is the best in the world. Our company is the best in the world.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <br><br>
    </div>

    <footer class="page-footer orange">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col l6 s12">
                    <h5 class="white-text">WSB-NLU</h5>
                    <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4"> I hate lorem ipsum :D </p>


                </div>
                <div class="col l3 s12">
                    <h5 class="white-text">Settings</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 1</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 2</a></li>
